So I was in Lyonesse killing pikeman, my trusty, cheese-loving pealldih sitting there eating cheese and looking out for me, and the call goes out that Excalibur was under attack. I decided to join the group and protect the relic - so I hopped on the horse and headed to Sauvage.  <P>After the long horse ride, I remembered the pet when I got to Castle Sauvage. Thinking that it may catch up to me since it was still onscreen with the run buff flashing, I waited.  Then I noticed that I had left him in the stay position.  Wow - guess I ought to release it and get something closer.  Instead, I hit the Follow button and I get the message<BR>You command the Peallidih to follow you!<P>Sure enough, after a few minutes wait (maybe 3?) and then going through the gates into the Forest Sauvage, my pet finally catches up to me just before reaching the first keep.<P>Now that is one loyal pet!<P>--------------------<P>Malachai Mindbender<BR>Enigmatic of Avalon - Guinivere<BR>Sanguis Societat<BR>http://www.farrout.net/sanguis/memberlist.asp?memberID=8
